T1  - WHY DO CHILDREN TAKE CARE OF THEIR ELDERLY PARENTS? ARE THE JAPANESE ANY DIFFERENT?
AU  - Horioka, Charles Yuji
AU  - Gahramanov, Emin
AU  - Hayat, Aziz
AU  - Tang, Xueli
Y1  - 2018/02/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12264
