T1  - UNIFIED CHINA AND DIVIDED EUROPE
AU  - Ko, Chiu Yu
AU  - Koyama, Mark
AU  - Sng, Tuan-Hwee
Y1  - 2018/02/01
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12270
